Step1: Go the Cluster in Databricks
Step2: Choose libraries
Step3: Install New
Step4: Select Library source as Maven
Step5: Under Cooridnates, click Search package
Step6: Change Spark package to Maven Package
Step7: In the Query Tab, Search Spark-excel
Step8: Select com.crealytics  - spark_excel_2.XX, where XX is your Scala version
Step9: Now in your Workspace use the code given in Code.scala
